<title>
Front Door Lock Assembly Inspection
</title>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Check that door opens and closes smoothly.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Check that door stops in the secondary latch position properly (preventing door from opening freely) and that door closes completely in the full latch position.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Adjust door latch striker position, if necessary. 
